OL,3,CMore than 5,000 NI children set to
OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FMore than 5,000 children in Northern
OL,8,FIreland are set to spend this
OL,9,FChristmas living in temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FIt has emerged that in November there
OL,13,Fwere 5,378 children in temporary
OL,14,Faccommodation, including 3,385 who
OL,15,Fwere aged nine and under.
OL,17,FThe number represents a 121% increase
OL,18,Fsince January 2019, when just over
OL,19,F2,433 children were living in
OL,20,Ftemporary accommodation.
