OL,3,CMore than 5,000 NI children set to
OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FIn total, some 4,908 households were
OL,8,Frecorded as living in temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation in November, more than
OL,10,Fdouble the 2,065 recorded in 2019.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, between April and
OL,13,FSeptember, 8,250 households presented
OL,14,Fto the Northern Ireland Housing
OL,15,FExecutive as homeless.
OL,17,FBelfast recorded the highest rate of
OL,18,Fpresentations with 7.5 presentations
OL,19,Fper 1,000 people (2,597 presentations
OL,20,Fin total between April and September).
