OL,3,CMore than 5,000 NI children set to
OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FThe capital was followed by Derry City
OL,8,Fand Strabane Council (960
OL,9,Fpresentations) which had a rate of 6.4
OL,10,Fand Mid and East Antrim Council area
OL,11,Fat 4.8.
OL,13,FNicola McCrudden, chief executive of
OL,14,FHomeless Connect, said the figures are
OL,15,Fshocking.
OL,17,F"In the run-up to the festive season,
OL,18,Fit should shock us all that more than
OL,19,F5,300 children are spending Christmas
OL,20,Fin temporary accommodation," she said.
