OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,F"I know that homelessness services who
OL,8,Fprovide accommodation and support will
OL,9,Fdo their very best to make this a
OL,10,Fhappy time and ensure that no one goes
OL,11,Fwithout. However, understandably, what
OL,12,Ffamilies really want is a home of
OL,13,Ftheir own.
OL,15,F"Sadly, for many experiencing
OL,16,Fhomelessness, having a place of their
OL,17,Fown is becoming an aspiration."
