OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FMs McCrudden said the rising numbers
OL,8,Fneeding temporary accommodation can be
OL,9,Fdirectly linked to the severe shortage
OL,10,Fof housing generally and social
OL,11,Fhousing more specifically.
OL,13,F"The main reason for families and
OL,14,Fsingle people presenting as homeless
OL,15,Fto the Housing Executive is that their
OL,16,Fcurrent accommodation is not suitable
OL,17,Ffor a variety of reasons including
OL,18,Fdisability, financial difficulty,
OL,19,Fviolence and overcrowding," she said.
