OL,3,CMore than 5,000 NI children set to
OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,F"Other significant factors include
OL,8,Fbreakdowns in sharing arrangements and
OL,9,Floss of rented accommodation ` which
OL,10,Fis becoming more frequent as many
OL,11,Ftenants struggle to meet rising rental
OL,12,Fcosts.
OL,14,F"In recent months, the Minister for
OL,15,FCommunities has announced a range of
OL,16,Fpositive measures including the
OL,17,Fpublication of a housing supply
OL,18,Fstrategy and his intention for a
OL,19,Fspecific allocation for homelessness
OL,20,Fprevention.
