OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,F"Homelessness is solvable. If we are
OL,8,Fto turn the curve on homelessness, we
OL,9,Fneed to increase housing supply and
OL,10,Faffordability ` including tackling
OL,11,Fissues of poverty.
OL,13,F"We need long-term, committed
OL,14,Finvestment in housing provision, in
OL,15,Fhomelessness prevention and funding
OL,16,Ffor key interventions to support
OL,17,Fpeople at the right time and in the
OL,18,Fright place."
