OL,4,Cspend Christmas in temporary
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,F"Between the failure to meet build
OL,8,Ftargets for social homes, the lack of
OL,9,Faffordability in the private rental
OL,10,Fsector, and increased cost-of- living
OL,11,Fpressures on households, there has
OL,12,Fbeen something of a 'perfect storm'
OL,13,Fcreated over the last few years which
OL,14,Fhas pushed many more families into
OL,15,Ftemporary accommodation.
